<td>The loan purpose is buying, building or renovating a property that will be owned by co-borrowers on the loan.</td>
<td>
<ul>
<li>If they will own equal or greater share of the property, then select <b>The borrower is receiving an equal or greater benefit on at least one loan purpose</b>.</li>
<li>If they are borrowing with their spouse and are structuring for asset protection, tax advantages or debt reduction, then select <b>The borrower will receive benefit due to spousal asset protection, tax advantages or debt reduction</b>.</li>
<li>If they have received independent financial, legal or accounting advice, then select <b>Independent financial, legal or accounting advice</b>.</li>
