<td>
<ul>
<li>If they are currently liable for an equal or greater share of the debt, then select <b>The borrower is receiving an equal or greater benefit on at least one loan purpose</b>.</li>
<li>If they are borrowing with their spouse and is structuring for asset protection, tax advantages or debt reduction, then select <b>The borrower will receive benefit due to spousal asset protection, tax advantages or debt reduction</b>.</li>
<li>If they have received independent financial, legal or accounting advice, then select <b>Independent financial, legal or accounting advice</b>.</li>
